title: Bitcoinking99
author: Bitcoinking99
content: Website         Twitter          Telegram           Telegram 1. The bounty campaign will be managed by  bitcoinking992. All participants must join Bounty telegram group: t.me/fomoinucoin3. Refrain from promoting talking about bounty programs in project chat groups. An immediate ban from company cha groups. Please ask your bounty-related questions in our bounty group.4. Please note that any offensive or inappropriate behavior may result in your being rejected.5. Using multiple accounts, cheating and spamming will get you disqualified from the bounty program and all your accounts will be permanently banned.6. Red Trust accounts will not be accepted in any way.7. All participants must submit their weekly reports to this bounty thread. For every week, you need to create new report. Anyone submitting the same work twice will be rejected.8. All participants must send the Proof of Authentication post to join the bounty program.Proof Of Registration Format (All participants must send 1 time):Code:#PROOF OF REGISTRATION              Forum Username:              Forum Profile Link:              Telegram Username:              Participated Campaigns:              BSC Wallet Address:BOUNTY ALLOCATIONTwitter _ 50%Telegram  _ 50% Week List Week 1 (03-08 _ 10-08)                          Rewards:1. Have more than 10,001 followers: 4 stakes/week                 Rules:  1. Every participant must follow mint mode Twitter page: https://twitter.com/fomoinucoin.2. Twitter accounts must have a minimum of 501 followers.3. Participants have to make new tweets or retweet 5 tweets per week (maximum 1 retweets/day).4. Time gap between 2 retweets/tweets needs to be 10 hours minimum.5. Participants must use hashtags: #Listing #CryptoExchange #Blockchain #ICO #finu Token  Join Here  Spreadsheet Rewards:5 stakes/weekRules:1. Update your Telegram name to Your Name | FINU  Ambassador. Officel  project group (Example:  | bitcoinking99 Ambassador)2. Participants can only wear one project name at a time. Wearing more than one project in your telegram name will disqualify you from the campaign.3. Your telegram username must be visible to all while in the community. You mustinteract with the Telegram account with which you have registered the campaign.Violation of this rule will lead to the removal of all earned stakes.4. You must wear FINU avatar and text until the end of the campaign to receive your stakes. Join Here  Spreadsheet
